Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.03,0:00:51.27,OP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}此刻從此開始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.55,0:00:53.91,OP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}試著想像一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.21,0:00:56.67,OP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}自己能做到什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.59,0:01:01.45,OP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}有出乎意料的變故
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.63,0:01:06.57,OP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}一定能夠越過
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.84,0:01:08.70,OP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}power of dream
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.81,0:01:11.94,OP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}一切從0開始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.15,0:01:17.42,OP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}閃耀著飛向明天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.53,0:01:19.22,OP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}light blue wind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.30,0:01:22.39,OP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}下定決心展翅飛翔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.65,0:01:28.80,OP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}用最美的笑容  出發！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.80,0:01:33.88,OP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}現在向未知的世界起飛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.73,0:01:40.20,OP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}未來的選擇  做決定的是自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.29,0:01:42.60,OP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}去追逐夢想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.70,0:01:44.16,OP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}也會有想哭的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.26,0:01:49.81,OP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}那是最重要的願望  不要走
